data.description: Welcome home to this gorgeous 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom family home in the coveted neighborhood of Santa Clarita. This home features beautiful manicured lawns with various rose bushes, cacti and palm trees. Upon entry through the foyer, you are met with high ceilings, natural light and an open floor plan displaying the living and dining room which leads to the open kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. This opens up to the den area featuring a beautiful brick fireplace. There is one main floor bedroom and bathroom. Laundry is tucked away in a hallway closet. Up the flight of stairs you will find the spacious master-suite behind double doors. There is a good sized balcony off the master suite overlooking the garden and mountain views. In the master ensuite bathroom, there is a huge soaking tub, dual vanity and spacious walk-in closet. Down the hall you will find an office area, two extra bedrooms with big windows, a full bathroom with double sinks.  The backyard features a beautiful fire pit with blue crystals and a heavy duty built-in BBQ grill. Surrounded by various high rated schools, shopping and restaurants .
